# TMAT - Tinggi Muka Air Tanah

## Pin Configuration

| Function  | GPIO   |
| --------- | ------ |
| Soil RX   | GPIO16 |
| Soil TX   | GPIO17 |
| I2C SDA   | GPIO8  |
| I2C SCL   | GPIO9  |
| SD CS     | GPIO10 |
| SD MOSI   | GPIO11 |
| SD MISO   | GPIO13 |
| SD SCK    | GPIO12 |
| AP Button | GPIO7  |

---

## Data Flow

Sensors
↓
Logger
↓
Local Processing
↓
SD Card Backup
↓
HTTPS Upload
↓
Cloud Server

If the server connection fails:

Sensors
↓
Logger
↓
SD Card Storage
↓
Automatic Replay After Reconnection

---

